{"data":[{"id":563855250,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"38fd1f8e97de27b5d9fc6ba74168bd02","url_token":"lu-ha-hua","name":"鲁哈花","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/ecfa3a89c645daad632756187ea1c4e4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/ecfa3a89c645daad632756187ea1c4e4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/38fd1f8e97de27b5d9fc6ba74168bd02","user_type":"people","headline":"进步使人难过","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":755,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563855250","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546302906,"updated_time":1546302906,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e“如果”，题目中提到“如果”，也就是说假设这是真的（不探讨是否是真的），被保送是小case。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当年陈景润证明了“1+2”，随着报告文学《哥德巴赫猜想》火遍大江南北，陈景润获得英雄般的荣誉，各种破格晋升接踵而至，研究员，人大代表，中央接见，出国访问，中科院院士，杂志主编等，组织上还给解决了个人问题，相信也得到了一流的医疗资源。陈景润完成这些的时候早已大学毕业，因此无法再将其擢升为大学生了，是不是好遗憾。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而陈景润做了什么贡献呢，就是1+2。是利用一种逼近的思路从9+9，6+6，。。。，1+3，1+2一路做过来的最好成果，下一步就是哥德巴赫猜想（1+1）了。但最新的学术意见认为，1+2和1+1之间，存在巨大的差距，已经达到了传统方法的极限，更进一步需要新的革命性的数学工具（在高中生未成名之前，我一个爱好者只能“被迫”选择相信这批卓越地位的数学家的言论）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这么说吧，哥德巴赫猜想是100分，那么9+9是25分，1+2从25分一路改进到了50分。我们的高中生从50分提升到了100分。仅凭这一点，同为破解希尔伯特问题成功者的一员，已经和怀尔斯（费马大定理），佩雷尔曼（庞加莱猜想）肩并肩了，远超陈景润，一个高中生超过40的可能性不大，收获菲尔兹奖板上钉钉，而且顺便打破最年轻获奖者记录。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果说怀尔斯，佩雷尔曼在公众印象中是一个单纯的难题破解者，我们的高中生则大大不同。前文说过，证明1+1需要新的数学工具，既然已经“如果”了，那么新的数学工具想必也一定诞生了，这才是更甚于\u003cb\u003e哥德巴赫-高中生名字定理\u003c/b\u003e的数学财富，必将引领一场或大或小的革命。这时候，我们的高中生就已经比肩欧几里得，欧拉，高斯，黎曼，牛顿，莱布尼茨等人了，很可能迫使数学家祖师爷前十排名发声变动，并顺便填补当代超级大师级数学家的空白。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说到这里还提保送就庸俗了，您可以发声质疑传统教育制度了，提出您的“钱学森之问”，教育部长肯定急一头汗。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这一切的发声都只需要让最开始的“如果”二字成真就可以了。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"“如果”，题目中提到“如果”，也就是说假设这是真的（不探讨是否是真的），被保送是小case。当年陈景润证明了“1+2”，随着报告文学《哥德巴赫猜想》火遍大江南北，陈景润获得英雄般的荣誉，各种破格晋升接踵而至，研究员，人大代表，中央接见，出国访问…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=231\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment